Simulation Scenario Notes

Current simulation uses a two-vehicle longitudinal driving scenario.

Scenario details:
- Target vehicle starts 30 m ahead
- Target vehicle initial speed = 8 m/s
- Controlled vehicle initial speed = 6 m/s
- Target vehicle slows down after step 120
- Controlled vehicle uses PID-based Adaptive Cruise Control to maintain safe distance

Future additions:
- Multiple driving scenarios
- Traffic disturbance cases
- Performance comparison plots
